Package: SpatialTranscriptomics
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Transcriptomics Analysis for IPF Research
Version: 0.1.0
Author: IPF Research Team
Maintainer: IPF Research Team <email@example.com>
Description: Comprehensive analysis tools for spatial transcriptomics data, 
    specifically designed for Idiopathic Pulmonary Fibrosis (IPF) research.
    Includes functions for cell type identification, overlap enrichment analysis,
    statistical comparisons, and gene signature scoring using GeoMx data.
